    <wsdl:operation name="OutageEventChangedNotification">
<wsdl:documentation xmlns:wsdl="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/">Publisher notifies subscriber of a change in OutageEvent by sending an array of changed OutageEvent objects.  GV returns information about failed transactions using an array of errorObjects. The message header attribute 'registrationID' should be added to all publish messages to indicate to the subscriber under which registrationID they received this notification data.</wsdl:documentation>
